<p>I have a question about changing the day automatically in the dropdown table. </p>  <p>The date for Monday is automatically set to the last Monday of the last month, and thats good. But now there's something else I want. When I change the date of Monday to 14 September 2015, then Tuesday should automaticaly change into 15 September, Wednesday to 16 etc.</p>  <p>How can that be accomplished?</p>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/4h8qr.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/4h8qr.png" alt="Current look"></a></p>  <pre><code>$(document).ready(function() { function getMonday(d)  { var day = d.getDay(); diff = d.getDate() - day + -6;  return new Date(d.setDate(diff)); }  var day = getMonday(new Date()); var month = day.getMonth()+1;  for(var i = 0; i &lt; 7; i++) { $('[name="start_day'+i+'"').val(day.getDate()+i); $('[name="start_month'+i+'"').val(month); } </code></pre>